videos.description: Spelling Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk can be almost as hard as the force he throws down an alley-oop dunk for Kansas.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk throws down massive alley-oop jam for Kansas in win

videos.description: Davon Dillard goes up for the block and gets called for the foul. Dillard starts talking and his teammate Phil Forte III comes over and covers his mouth in Oklahoma State's loss to Kansas.
